## Config System

```php
// conf/config.php (site-specific, NOT config-defaults.php)
$Configuration['Garden']['CurrentTheme'] = 'spotify';
$Configuration['themeFeatures']['DataDrivenTheme'] = true;
$Configuration['Garden']['HomepageTitle'] = 'Spotify Community';
$Configuration['Garden']['Authenticator']['DefaultScheme'] = 'oauth2';
$Configuration['EnabledPlugins']['QnA'] = true;
$Configuration['EnabledPlugins']['ideation'] = true;
$Configuration['Feature']['CustomLayouts']['home'] = true;
$Configuration['HotReload']['Enabled'] = true;  // Dev only
```

## Dev Environment

```bash
# Clone and set up
git clone <vanilla-local>
cd vanilla-local

# Docker dev environment
docker compose up -d

# Install deps
composer install
yarn install

# Create a local site
./cli/bin/vnla spawn-site

# Build frontend
yarn build       # Production
yarn build:dev   # Dev with HMR

# Run tests
vendor/bin/phpunit
yarn test:unit
```

Dev site accessible at `https://vanilla.local/<sitename>`.

