## Deploy Process

No CI/CD. Deploy via Vanilla's "Theme Pull" in forum dashboard:
1. Push code to the appropriate branch (`master`/`stage`/`develop`)
2. Go to dashboard Settings > Theme
3. Click "Theme Pull" to deploy from GitHub
4. `deploy.json` maps branches to site IDs
